MYS GIVEAWAY❗️Get a chance to win a FREE Monaco Yacht Show entrance tickets! 

This year they are worth 500€ ! Join the most exclusive and influential event of the year! 

Instructions to participate: follow @genoasuperyachthub, @theyachtmogul @onboardwithmarcela, and comment why are you a yachting fan, and tag three friends u wanna go with! 

Winners will be announced Sunday 19th on @genoasuperyachthub 

This is an initiative from @Genoasuperyachthub by @amicorefitshipyard and @pestoseagroup in collab with @onboardwithmarcela 

📸 @yvangrubski
